{"type":null,"faqId":22421,"title":"如何使用手机控制华为盒子？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in;}\n.p1{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.19722222in;margin-left:0.31527779in;margin-top:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p4{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.36805555in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<a name=\"screen_1_sec3_p1\"></a><span>请按照如下步骤操作：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1  </span><span>将手机和华为盒子连接至同一家庭网络。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1  </span><span>在“</span><span class=\"s2\">设置 &gt; 网络 &gt; 网络状态</span><span>”中找到华为盒子的 IP 地址。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=74443\" style=\"width:4.3305554in;height:2.4270833in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1  </span><span>扫描二维码，添加盒子的微信公众号。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">华为荣耀盒子</span><span>公众号</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=74444\" style=\"width:1.075in;height:1.075in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1  </span><span>在手机上打开微信公众号，选择“</span><span class=\"s2\">应用 </span><span>&gt; </span><span class=\"s2\">遥控器</span><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1  </span><span>输入华为盒子 IP 地址，点击连接。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>此时，您将能使用微信上的遥控器控制华为盒子。</span><a name=\"screen_1_sec3_p2\"><a name=\"gen_id1_11_3_3_3_1_1\"><a name=\"gen_id1_11_3_3_3_1_2\"><a name=\"gen_id1_11_3_3_3_1_3\"></a></a></a></a><a name=\"screen_1_sec3_p2\"><a name=\"gen_id1_11_3_3_3_1_1\"><a name=\"gen_id1_11_3_3_3_1_2\"><a name=\"gen_id1_11_3_3_3_1_3\"></a></a></a></a>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":246,"faqType":"遥控","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"6301","faqTypeCode":"Media_Device-Remote","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1428628513000,"seriesProductName":"MediaQ M330","visitedTimes":141,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"M330,MediaQ M330,华为盒子,手机遥控,微信遥控","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}